    • autoFillEnchantConfig

      public static void autoFillEnchantConfig​(org.bukkit.enchantments.Enchantment enchant, java.lang.String desc, java.lang.Integer cost)
      Deprecated.
      Automatically fills the max level, scrap value, upgrade material, upgrade description, cost type, cost start value and value of the specified enchant for easier value setting. Max level is set to 10, scrap value is set to half cost, upgrade icon is set to BOOK, upgrade description is set to the specified description (so people can understand what the enchant does), the cost type is set to linear and the start value and value is set to the specified cost.
      Parameters:
      enchant - The enchant to fill
      desc - The description to fill
      cost - The cost you want to set
